Convert system deployment

1. Install ffmpeg
2. Add ffmpeg home directory to %FFMPEG_HOME% variable
3. Add %FFMPEG_HOME%\bin to %PATH% variable

4. Install Java JDK 8+

5. Add scripts home (folder "convert") to %CONVERT_HOME% variable
6. Add %CONVERT_HOME%\win to %PATH% variable
7. Add %CONVERT_HOME%\lin to %PATH% variable

8. Install ImageMagic to process images
